    "**비교 — AWS ECS/Fargate on-demand**\n",
    "\n",
    "- 현재: min 1 task × 0.5 vCPU × 1Gi × 24h × 30d ≈ $18 + ALB $16 + Secrets $0.4 + DB $15 → **$50+/월** (트래픽 0에도 상시 비용)\n",
